Contents:

README          this file
thesis-IK.tex   main file to work on
thesis-IK.bib   the bibliography file
structure.tex   specifies settings of the thesis (including support for Dutch if you need this)
ruglogo.pdf     logo for the cover page
ruglogo-nl.pdf  Dutch version of logo
aclnatbib.bst   bibliography style file

How to compile:

% pdflatex thesis-IK
% bibtex thesis-IK
% pdflatex thesis-IK
% pdflatex thesis-IK

This should give the file thesis-IK.pdf
